title: Data vs  Gut
description:
So today lets talk about the power of intuition. For many it's straight line thinking, data or intuition (gut feeling) but in reality data doesn't give you a persons intent or work ethic and intuition doesn't give you the data to prove feasibility. A lot is possible when armed with both and when armed with both, take action!
